---
const CertificatesImages = import.meta.glob('../assets/images/certificates/*', {
  eager: true,
});

---
<div class="hero bg-neutral/70 min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-evenly" id="certificates">
    <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-secondary">Certificates</h3>
<div class="grid grid-cols-3 p-3  gap-5 justify-evenly">
  {Object.values(CertificatesImages).map((img) =>{
    const src = (img as any).default;
    return <div class="card bg-base-100  shadow-lg max-h-106">
        <figure class="max-h-60">
          <img src={src['src']} alt="certificate image" />
        </figure>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title">{src['src'].toString().split('/').pop().split('_').pop().split('.')[0]} certificate</h2>
          {src['src'].toString().includes('CS50x') ?
            <p>An in-depth computer science program covering algorithms, data structures, C programming, memory management, problem-solving, and software engineering practices. 
              Completed all problem sets, labs, and the final capstone project, gaining strong foundational CS knowledge.
            </p> :
            src['src'].toString().includes('CS50P') ?
            <p>
              A comprehensive Python programming course focused on real-world applications, clean code, debugging, functions, OOP, unit testing, file I/O, and problem-solving. 
              Completed nine structured problem sets and a final project demonstrating practical Python development skills.
            </p>
          :
            src['src'].toString().includes('mongo') ?
            <p>
              An introductory course in MongoDB, covering database concepts, CRUD operations, collections, documents, indexing, and working with NoSQL data models. 
              Gained practical knowledge using MongoDB tools and shell commands, preparing for backend and full-stack development workflows.
            </p>
          :
            <p>ŸêA foundational course covering the core concepts and principles of database management. This certification signifies a solid understanding of fundamental database 
              structures, terminologies, and design concepts necessary for further specialization in data management and development.</p>
          }
          
        </div>
      </div>
  })}
  
</div>
</div>